{"tid":1249564,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再講國際法庭, 根本唔可行","createTime":"2019-06-21T18:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T18:31:12.000Z","uid":262154,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3f92ebb556425b86e90558cd82c41509e890e340","tid":1249564,"uid":262154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:05:44.000Z","msg":"國際法庭, 其實有兩個, <br />\n1) 一個係聯合國機構, ICJ, 兩個國家之間可以仲裁, 唔管刑事<br />\n2) 一個唔係聯合國機構, 叫國際刑事法庭, 要簽約加入, 管刑事 (戰爭, 反人道, 種族滅絕, 侵略, 同反公義), 大家應該係講呢個<br />\n 國際刑事法庭管轄權如下:<br />\n1) 係締約國裡面犯法<br />\n2)  締約國嘅人/ 組織犯法<br />\n3) 安理會可以批准嘅單次指定嘅範圍<br />\n<br />\n問題係, 中國唔係締約國, 即係(1) 同 (2) 都唔適用, 至於 (3) 靠安理會決議, 即係要中國唔反對 (中國係安理會有絶對反對權), <br />\n<br />\n即係無辦法"},{"pid":"5c358de239cf52ecb3973ce3d789e575e2cbc346","tid":1249564,"uid":215864,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:11:13.000Z","msg":"叫美國重組聯合國"},{"pid":"a59889517e07dd6f8117c4ee8a5e372bf0937268","tid":1249564,"uid":228437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:16:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化！！！</span></span></strong></strong>"},{"pid":"f4875f2ae3765edfb9c302b4bd3628bfa1131a9c","tid":1249564,"uid":132128,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:17:47.000Z","msg":"唱聖詩應該有用d"},{"pid":"328a47c7117aa6f07fa442c9a0a875bdbef5ca5a","tid":1249564,"uid":5574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:18:00.000Z","msg":"攪左先, 上到安理會都好呀 !"},{"pid":"ea42b09a99b76d180abe19064b39d2eaa313d133","tid":1249564,"uid":234835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:18:43.000Z","msg":"推到上國際層面 推到班警犬比人武器禁運"},{"pid":"a5c9298ca484419c58cb98e681a81483e74ce8d8","tid":1249564,"uid":262154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c358de239cf52ecb3973ce3d789e575e2cbc346","tid":1249564,"uid":215864,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:11:13.000Z","msg":"叫美國重組聯合國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:19:23.000Z","msg":"美國都無簽約 (但係當年的左南斯拉夫上去審）"},{"pid":"4430d124d0b06fa6864c05028e11deee76e86091","tid":1249564,"uid":141359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:21:35.000Z","msg":"玩到佢地出唔到國 永享大灣區榮耀"},{"pid":"1ffec44d6dedd953c31cfa7748f71020726edc1c","tid":1249564,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:21:59.000Z","msg":"咁我諗試下推上國際層面<br />\n好過試都唔試掛？"},{"pid":"72b9a42a198615ca14ecb055750247de69efd9bb","tid":1249564,"uid":27415,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f4875f2ae3765edfb9c302b4bd3628bfa1131a9c","tid":1249564,"uid":132128,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:17:47.000Z","msg":"唱聖詩應該有用d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sad but true"},{"pid":"755149bc94ed600670dfcbde07a21c9cb73de4b0","tid":1249564,"uid":262154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ffec44d6dedd953c31cfa7748f71020726edc1c","tid":1249564,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:21:59.000Z","msg":"咁我諗試下推上國際層面<br />\n好過試都唔試掛？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:24:59.000Z","msg":"可以推, 但唔係國際法庭,<br />\n應該FOCUS 係歐盟同美國《香港人權民主法案》"},{"pid":"992981076bbe82ee52844601006f6a4974e3f99d","tid":1249564,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:31:12.000Z","msg":"「即係要中國唔反對 (中國係安理會有絶對反對權), 」<br />\n如果可以推到去中國反對嗰步<br />\n起碼都叫做幫我地免費宣傳一次中共點打壓我地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者咁講 歐美個法案係主要<br />\n國際法庭係次要"}]}